<plot>All in is the story of four friends. Ian and Tony (Caucasian brothers) and Bal &amp; Gary, (soon to be brother in laws of East Indian descent). A guy's night out, having some beers, playing poker, just like any other night. But this night eventually leads the friends to discover that they might not know each other as well as they had thought. The recent announcement of Gary's arranged engagement has left each of the guys with something to say. When the matter comes up and gets too intense it seems like a clashing of cultural backgrounds, but we discover that there's more to the debate than just that.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?030720</url></doc>
